title: Walking Pad, Walking Treadmill Under Desk Treadmill for Home with Remote Control
item_description:
Walking Pad, Walking Treadmill Under Desk Treadmill for Home with Remote Control
Product details

【Under Desk Treadmill 2 in 1】The speed range of treadmill is 0.6-3.8mph, and adjusts each time 0.2mph, so it is not only for walking while you are working, but also for jogging when you are free.
